20 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
21 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of a new law not to be
22 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
23 This act shall be known and may be cited as the “High Voltage
24 Electric Transmission Facility Act”.
